import React, {Component} from "react"
import { Form, Checkbox, Button, Header, Image, Modal } from 'semantic-ui-react'

export default class CreateModal extends Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)

    this.state = {

    }
    open: useState(false)
    setOpen: useState(false)
  }


render () {
  return (
    <Modal
      onClose={() => setOpen(false)}
      onOpen={() => setOpen(true)}
      open={open}
      trigger={<Button>Add Goal</Button>}
    >
      <Modal.Header>Add a New Goal</Modal.Header>


      <Modal.Content>
            <Form>

                <Form.Field>
                  <label>Goal Name</label>
                  <input placeholder='Goal Name' />
                </Form.Field>

                <Form.Field>
                  <label>Tier 1 Column Headers (e.g. Days or Sessions)</label>
                  <input placeholder='Separated,By,Commas' />
                </Form.Field>

                <Form.Field>
                  <label>Tier 2 Column Headers (e.g. Steps per Session/Day)</label>
                  <input placeholder='Separated,By,Commas' />
                </Form.Field>

                <Form.Field>
                  <label>Row Labels (e.g. Week Dates, Week #'s, Repetion Labels)</label>
                  <input placeholder='Separated,By,Commas' />
                </Form.Field>



        <Button type='submit'>Submit</Button>
      </Form>
      </Modal.Content>


      <Modal.Actions>
        <Button color='black' onClick={() => setOpen(false)}>
          Nevermind
        </Button>
        <Button
          content="Looks good!"
          labelPosition='right'
          icon='checkmark'
          onClick={() => setOpen(false)}
          positive
        />
      </Modal.Actions>
    </Modal>
  )

}


}
